Spawn Characteristics

Energy Sources-  Main Resource

	Energy Sources
		Harvested by worker creeps
		limited
		Recharge every 5 minutes

Spawns- The HQ
	Spawns
		Max 3 per room
		Ability to store energy
		Summon units
		Default: 300 energy units , allowing only regular creeps

	Spawn Extension
		max Storage: 50 energy points
